general:
Available commands: 
    /help - Displays this message
-=Chemistry of the elements=-
    /sym [symbol/name] - Symbol or name of the element
    /mp [symbol] - Shows the melting point
    /bp [symbol] - Shows the boiling point
    /year [symbol] - Shows the year of discovery
    /os [symbol] - Shows the possible oxidation states
    /config [symbol] - Shows the electronic configuration
    /density [symbol] - Shows the density
-=General chemistry=-
    /mw [formula] - Calculate molar mass
    /mass [L, M, formula] - Grams needed for xL yM solution
    /molar [g, L, formula] - Calculates molarity of solution
    /volume [g, M formula] - L needed for yM solution from xgms
    /synonym [molecule] - Gives up to 5 synonyms for a compound
    /prop [molecule] - Gives various general properties a compound
    /medchem [molecule] - Various medicinal chemistry properties
    /cas [molecule] - Retrieves the CAS number of a compound
-=Other commands=-
    /eval [JavaScript] - Evaluate JavaScript
    /killeval - Kill sandbox process
    /wis [formula] - Calculator
    /geoip [ip] - Shows location of server
    /sim - Nigger SimCity 3000
    /rpg [buy, sell, make, bribe, stats] - Drug RPG
    /n - Nigger synonyms
    /kek - Nigger jokes
    /shout [text] - SHOUT!!!
    /jew - Display random swastikas
    /apple - Display random apples
